Is there a way to check our older pixels fro the event management page?    For example I would like to grab our Gundry ROAS pixel and have our developer take a look....

To check your older pixels in the Event Management page, you can log into your Ad Manager account and navigate to Tools >> Event Management. From there, you should be able to see a list of all your existing pixels, including the Gundry ROAS pixel. If you need to grab specific details or settings for your developer, just click on the pixel name to view its configuration. Let me know if you need any more help with this!
